get.description:
Search for the best bookable flight offers from a very simple query where you can specify as little as the travel origin, a destination and a departure date.

### Query example
What are the best offers for flights from New-York to Madrid the 1st of October 2020?
<pre><code>
GET https://test.api.amadeus.com/v1/shopping/flight-offers?origin=NYC&destination=MAD&departureDate=2020-10-01&max=2
</code></pre>

